---
description: Rules for packages/core and packages/schema
globs: packages/core/**,packages/schema/**
alwaysApply: false
---

- Scene schema is the source of truth.
- Prefer Zod schemas and generated JSON-schema-compatible contracts.
- Reducers must be pure and deterministic.
- No UI concerns inside core.
- Preserve no-op reference equality when possible.
- Protect against invalid states: cycles, orphan nodes, invalid selection.